servlet

Class WebReqHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • servlet.WebReqHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    @WebServlet(value="/WebReqHandler")
public class WebReqHandler
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    Servlet implementation class WebReqHandler This servlet handles all the incoming requests for fractal plotting and iteration plotting. It further calls respective methods of ScriptRequHandler and redirects to the same page along with the url of plotted image.
